--- Server API Endpoints (Workers) ---
File: crates/server/src/routes/workers.rs
- POST /workers/register → register_worker()
- GET /workers → list_workers() - paginated, returns PaginatedResponse<WorkerSummary>
- GET /workers/:id → get_worker() - returns WorkerDetail
- DELETE /workers/:id → delete_worker() - reclaims jobs, returns 204
- POST /workers/:id/heartbeat → heartbeat()

--- Server API Endpoints (Logs) ---
File: crates/server/src/routes/logs.rs
- POST /workers/tasks/:id/logs → ingest_logs()
- GET /sessions/:id/logs → get_session_logs() - filters: limit, cursor, job_id, level, last
- DELETE /sessions/:id/logs → delete_session_logs() - optional job_id filter
- GET /sessions/:id/logs/stream → stream_session_logs() (SSE) - filters: job_id, level

